{"id":"holomush-e41x.5","title":"cache_test_helpers.go in production package is importable by production code","description":"internal/access/policy/cache_test_helpers.go is a non-test file in the production policy package (no _test.go suffix, package policy declaration). This means NewCacheWithPoliciesForTest is exported from the production package and is callable from any production code that imports internal/access/policy. The lint:test-helpers task only catches policytest imports, not imports of the production policy package.

