{"id":"holomush-0hag.4","title":"plugin subscriber.go EmitPluginEvent still uses slog.Error without context","description":"In internal/plugin/subscriber.go deliverAsync(), the error log for EmitPluginEvent at line ~13231 still uses slog.Error (context-free) instead of slog.ErrorContext(tctx, ...). The PR changes the surrounding code to use tctx for DeliverEvent and EmitPluginEvent calls, but the error handler for the EmitPluginEvent failure was not updated to use ErrorContext.

