{"id":"holomush-wfza.16","title":"cache_export.go ships test helper in production binary","description":"internal/access/policy/cache_export.go is a regular .go file (not _test.go), so NewCacheWithPoliciesForTest() is compiled into production binaries and exported to any importer of the policy package.

